import random
lives = 3
rand1=0
rand2=0
ans1=0
realans=0
print("I am the linear equation monster and will test you on your mathematical skills, you are allowed ",lives," wrong attempts and if youre wrong you will pay with your life")
print("Level 1: ")
rand1=random.randint(0,9)
rand2=random.randint(0,9)
realans=rand1+rand2
print(rand1,"+",rand2,"=")
ans1=int(input())
if realans == ans1:
    print("uGh that was correct but you wont get the next one!")
if realans != ans1:
    print("HaH You lose 1 life")
    lives-=-1
